premise_source_doc_sentence: Everfest is an Austin-based company that connects the festival community online .
Festival-goers can find worldwide festivals , connect with friends , build a calendar and share content about festival experiences .

Festival organizers work with Everfest to manage their online presence and market their event to attendees , including a perk system that allows organizers to provide discounts or free items to festival-goers .
Everfest includes festivals of all types , grouping them across 12 categories : art , book , civic , cultural , faith , food , film , historical , music , performance , seasonal and unique .
The platform uses an algorithm to recommend festivals to festival-goers based on their likes and locations , as well as festivals they prefer or have attended previously .
